snippet.textDisplay: That was originally a naat, but modifications in lyrics made it hamd as in the beginning he says ishq e haqiqui khaliq e alam (real love, creator of the world). I would prefer to go with the original subject but its OK even if you praise your God. Music persuades strangers to listen what you believe and that's a great thing.

snippet.textDisplay:
Ali Sethi's "maula" at 1:00 is everything I wished to happen in Coke Studio: unlimited goosebumps. I want this multi-talented guy to make a spectacular breakthough in the music industry and wash our ears from the accumulated aural dirt throughout the recent years.
On repeat - 3:40
اے میرے مالک میرے خالق میرے حاجت روا
جب نہیں ہو ساتھ کوئی بس تیرا ہے آسرا
چھائے کہیں جو گہرا اندھیرا
تیری عطا سے آئے سویرا
تیری ہی خلقت چاند تارے
تو نے ہی بخشی یہ روشنی ہے
Ufffff. Goosebumps. <3

Hello Everyone,
what is this yaar? ye ek Naat hai or hum ye Naat ko kis trha sun rahay hen? No doubt Abida Parveen hamari legend hen or cokestudio jesa music kahen nahi par iska matlab ye tow nahi k hum dusri cheezen bhool jaen.. aaj hum log ye kahengy yaar theek hai Naat hai tow kya hua hai or apni daleel dene lag jaynge bs ek cheez pe gor karen jese jese ye cheezen aam horahe hen hamari soch bi usi trha badalti jaa rahi hai agay phr aesi koi cheez hogi ya kch bi uspe bhi hum yehi kahengy yaar khair hogai.. Zara sab sochen k aaj hum is waqt kahan kharay hen Where we are standing today? Ye sab cheezen aese aam na hone do.
ALLAH hum sab musalmano ko Naik hidayat de.
